        public EntityViewLinkBuilder association(@NonNull
                                         @NonNull EntityConfiguration targetConfiguration)
        Description copied from class: SingleEntityViewLinkBuilder
        Create a link builder for an association. Will use the first non-hidden association for the target configuration. If there is more than one, you should use SingleEntityViewLinkBuilder.association(String) instead.

        If there is no actual EntityAssociation available, the name will be interpreted as a regular EntityConfiguration instead and a link builder with a from parameter will be returned to the target entity configuration.
